3
00:00:03,920 --> 00:00:06,890
Sometimes we want to say
something loudly and clearly,

4
00:00:06,890 --> 00:00:09,790
or with a little bit of emotion.

5
00:00:09,790 --> 00:00:10,900
Quit it.

6
00:00:10,900 --> 00:00:13,920
Sometimes we, cut it out.

7
00:00:13,920 --> 00:00:17,350
Sometimes when we're trying, stop it.

8
00:00:17,350 --> 00:00:20,630
Sometimes we're trying to make a point,

9
00:00:20,630 --> 00:00:23,800
we say things very clearly
and directly to people.

10
00:00:23,800 --> 00:00:27,400
Again, we say these when
we're speaking with emotion.

11
00:00:27,400 --> 00:00:30,310
We say these, when we
want to speak loudly,

12
00:00:30,310 --> 00:00:32,369
because someone is far away,

13
00:00:32,369 --> 00:00:35,650
or we say these in a way that
just communicates strongly

14
00:00:35,650 --> 00:00:36,770
what we're feeling.

15
